starburstenterprise.title: Starburst Enterprise
starburstenterprise.description: Starburst Enterprise platform (SEP) is the commericial distribution of Trino, which is an open-source, Massively Parallel Processing (MPP) ANSI SQL query engine. Starburst simplifies data access for your RHODS workloads by providing fast access to all of your data, no matter where it lives. Starburst does this by connecting directly to each data source and pulling the data back into memory for processing, alleviating the need to copy or move the data into a single location first.
